packets.name: PIXLwear P1 Sneaker (Black/Charcoal), right
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: The PIXLwear P1 sneaker is a Cryptovoxels shoe for every situation. Comfortable, yet stylish. High-quality, yet affordable. The P1 model rocks the iconic PIXLwear colours for the tie-free laces and on the sides, and of course the PIXL P1 stamp on the sole. The insoles feature a clever P1 design wrapping onto the back of the shoe. This is the right shoe in the black/charcoal colour. Designer: Pixls.eth. Manufactured with MagicaVoxel. PIXLwear (a PIXL brand) - ethical blockchain fashion from Austria.
